snippet.title: Xcode 10 New Feature: Image Literal - Picking Assets in Code
snippet.description:
Selecting images in Xcode 10 has becoming increasingly difficult an frustrating. Let me show you how you can use "Image Literal" to pick the assets from your catalog.  It's extremely buggy but it certainly gets the job done. Enjoy.
